# Shimada RubyKaigi

## Keynote
- Koji Shimada

## Details
### Date
- October 27, 2012 (open: 13:00, close: 16:35)

### Venue
- Shibuya (The details will be announced later)

- Please contact the sponsors of the event.

### Schedule
- 13:30-14:30 Keynote (Koji Shimada)

### Official Party

- Naoto Takai (Organizing director)
